snippet.title: Frogun - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Renata as she adventures across a world of mystical ruins with the titular FROGUN! Frogun is an old-school platformer with the soul of the PS1/N64 era, in which your frog-shaped grappling hook is a your best friend!  Coming to PC/Mac/Linux, Nintendo Switch, PS4/5, and Xbox in 2022! 



Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1575470/Frogun/
Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/molegato/frogun
